OP02-OP02-001 foil.name: Edward.Newgate (OP02-001)
OP02-OP02-001 foil.Description: [End of Your Turn] Add 1 card from the top of your Life cards to your hand.

OP02-OP02-008.name: Jozu
OP02-OP02-008.Description:
[DON!! x1] If you have 2 or less Life cards and your Leader's type includes "Whitebeard Pirates", this Character gains [Rush].

(This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)

OP02-OP02-018.name: Marco
OP02-OP02-018.Description:
(After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)

[On K.O.] You may trash 1 card with a type including "Whitebeard Pirates" from your hand: If you have 2 or less Life cards, play this Character card from your trash rested.

OP02-OP02-019.name: Rakuyo
OP02-OP02-019.Description: [DON!! x1] [Your Turn] All of your Characters with a type including "Whitebeard Pirates" gain +1000 power.

OP03-OP03-003.name: Izo
OP03-OP03-003.Description: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 card with a type including "Whitebeard Pirates" other than [Izo] and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

OP03-OP03-010.name: Fossa
OP03-OP03-010.Description: [Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)

ST15-ST15-001.name: Atmos
ST15-ST15-001.Description: [When Attacking] If your Leader is [Edward.Newgate], you cannot add Life cards to your hand using your own effects during this turn.

ST15-ST15-002 foil.name: Edward.Newgate (ST15-002)
ST15-ST15-002 foil.Description:
[On Play] Give up to 1 rested DON!! card to your Leader or 1 of your Characters.

[Activate: Main] You may rest this Character: K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 5000 power or less.

ST15-ST15-003.name: Kingdew
ST15-ST15-003.Description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)

[Opponent's Turn] When this Character is K.O.'d by an effect, up to 1 of your Leader gains +2000 power during this turn.

ST15-ST15-004.name: Thatch
ST15-ST15-004.Description: [On Play] If your Leader's type includes "Whitebeard Pirates", give up to 1 of your opponent's Characters 2000 power during this turn. Then, add 1 card from the top of your Life cards to your hand.

ST15-ST15-005 foil.name: Portgas.D.Ace
ST15-ST15-005 foil.Description:
If your Leader's type includes "Whitebeard Pirates", this Character gains [Rush].

(This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)

[Once Per Turn] If this Character would be removed from the field by your opponent's effect, you may give this Character 2000 power during this turn instead.
